Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========OP==========
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:12.33,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是连前进轨道都无法改变的几率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:16.86,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有百分之一就要奋起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:20.70,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟、被「命运」所束缚的人生、不 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:27.38,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要将它重写、因为若能看见你和未来 不是最棒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:30.48,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧！我只想在战斗中成长 HEY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:31.31,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,击穿阴天！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:34.48,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我的烈焰仍旧熊熊燃烧 雷鸣撕裂天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:38.32,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想消除梦魇 看见未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:40.79,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,过去、未来、还有如今当下、
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:43.78,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不畏惧过去 现在为了被托付的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:45.13,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吼出我的骄傲!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:51.80,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想看到眼泪、所以要不断嘶吼！一直永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:55.80,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会堕落！因为扬起的风会让我凌驾于命运之上！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:03:02.18,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因为身后、有着想要守护的笑容！ 永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.65,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,为了彼此！我会揍飞你心中的痛苦！让悲伤什么的永远安息！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:09.78,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,832)}无论多少次…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:34.95,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,月光摇曳 我们未来的蓝图
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:42.17,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会实现 描绘明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:47.01,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不会磨灭 铭记在心中的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:55.81,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,若是无尽的泪水能掩盖伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:04.82,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,那就无需畏惧 再次去相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:13.32,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,向着无边无际的天空 张开双臂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:19.16,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不再哭泣 仰望天空中那轮皎月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:24.96,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,即使心存悲伤 也要怀着希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:29.30,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算无法回头 也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:35.93,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生辉的梦想 闪耀在探索的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:41.94,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,最宝贵的那份思念 仍旧在延续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:47.78,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪里 我们都一起走过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:55.45,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,825)}握住那唯一的心灵之匙吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Avant==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的希望之门打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜利之门打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 未来就能得救了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从未来而来的露西小姐也能安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能打开门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须现在立刻关上门
Comment: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,==========Main==========
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻关上门 那扇门不能打开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大门会关上 这是已经决定好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:51.79,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(640,450)\fad(524,0}连我的份一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关上门 立刻马上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 这是对抗大龙群的唯一兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在关上门的话 日蚀·加农炮将无法发射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么日蚀·加农炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是一扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连结时间的门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将自身积蓄的魔力释放出来的武器就是日蚀·加农炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 那根本不是什么武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再说下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然会受到公主的惩戒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那扇大门是连接400年前的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地面震动得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力？不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是城堡的方向 也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个日蚀启动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙…从门里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是城堡的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然如此强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧 这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能打得过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有一头出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事啊 又有龙冒出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门要怎样才能关上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说啊 现在不是发呆的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边的底座上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,底座 就是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要搬动这个扳手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用星灵魔法师的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一万头龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是从门里出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 你刚刚是察觉到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我 是克鲁爷爷一直在调查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就在刚才终于完成了对这个门的分析
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是将泽雷夫之书的魔法和星灵魔法相调和而成的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是可以通过指定时间的坐标来进行时间移动的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天是个例外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个月亮会扰乱它的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法错乱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 这扇门才会失去控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它和400年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是和龙族仍然存活的时代连接到了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话…和之前说的不一样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是…如何形容这样的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的吧 这样的有一万头？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快散开 找个地方隐蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则会被一举击溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出来一头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是岩石 岩石在动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 门还是关不上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙一头接一头的跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么关不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 这里危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于我错误的决策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界迎来了终结…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界…将被龙的愤怒浸染
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要连另一个我的份儿一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我的份一起欢笑 一起哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地震…难道已经？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答应过她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有龙从门里出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点关上门的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请快点回避
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 请抓紧时间回避
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这究竟是做了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 快点把门关上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星灵魔法师的力量不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西小姐 请拿出黄道十二门的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我的钥匙一起 用十二把钥匙把门封印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用星灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钥匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发出金光…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄道十二门的星灵们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请借给我封印邪恶之物的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开启吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二门的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄道十二宫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 所有的星灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高兴还太早了 出来了几头龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七 七头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不错啊 露西 雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有七头龙就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格…大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话 我还真控制不了一万头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个人…告知了我未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是欺骗了公主的未来人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你最开始的目的就是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好听着 愚民们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始 人类的时代宣告终结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来即将展开的是龙的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为开始 就将这个城镇里的所有魔法师杀个干净吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙听那家伙的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚他说控制什么的…难道说？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是支配龙的秘术 操龙魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支配龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的目的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做这种事有什么好处…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给你了 基尔柯尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是挺好吃的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在龙之墓地见到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这 这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体是由火焰构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固定好脚边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按计划好的做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾名为阿特拉斯弗莱姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让汝等见识地狱之炎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住 小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑齿之虎总攻击 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯着嘴里 肚子 那些好像很软的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Man 这就是真正的龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才是展现我们蓝色天马实力的好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用人数压倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有魔力全放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点伤都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中一点攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃这招 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好结实的生物 任何魔法都不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中攻击某一点试试如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家协作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我先砍他一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐殿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 快散开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Man
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然施加了防御力下降的香气 还是没用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Man
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 连一点擦伤都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳞片居然如此坚固
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是否能打倒龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再肆虐一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们看看龙之怒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏·多拉格尼尔…
Comment: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Preview==========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:24:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 那么强大的龙居然有七头
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 哈比 吓尿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱才没有害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是正好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙有七头 我们这边也有七位灭龙魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？ 不是只有六位灭龙魔法师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 数个数你都不会么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我当傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有第七位在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 七头龙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的一位 怎么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.31,0:24:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？ 莫非是那个家伙？
